text: Visidela (The Fishing Net) () is a 1997 Sri Lankan romantic drama movie directed by H.D. Premaratne and starring W. Jayasiri, Anusha Sonali, Jackson Anthony, Daya Thennakoon, Daya Alwis, Robin Fernando, Mahendra Perera. ==Other websites== * at IMDB Category:1997 romantic drama movies Category:Sri Lankan movies Category:Movies directed by H.D.
